GameTips: {
	SpiritGameTip0: Moon Jelly makes a great source of healing!
	SpiritGameTip1: Overseer isn't coming back!
	SpiritGameTip2: You can find the Adventurer in the Underground Briar at any time.
	SpiritGameTip3: Mystic Shrines offer many benefits - or threats!
	SpiritGameTip4: The Jem holds power untold. Do you have what it takes?
	SpiritGameTip5: Defeat the Starplate Voyager to obtain Astralite, a powerful space metal.
	SpiritGameTip6: The Ocean is full of many surprises. Check it out sometime!
	SpiritGameTip7: Clubs make for really nice short range weapons, especially if you need to keep a lot of enemies off of you.
	SpiritGameTip8: The Sepulchres deep underground are dangerous, but well worth it.
	SpiritGameTip9: Quests are an easy way to get a ton of rewards - talk to the Adventurer to get the book!
}

